Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小… 不 久川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像以前那樣叫我小袋就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣太生疏了 阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被這樣叫還是頭一回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 雪集 你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽復活了 回到仁太身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到現在還…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 宿海他說小芽怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 仁太 很久不見還是那麼強大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海他說小芽怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他所是幻聽嗎 還是幻想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是說小芽想實現願望之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕 睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽 你回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 幹嘛去洗澡 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸還沒出門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 毛巾只有黑褐色的 小芽不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 稍微注意下自己身體的成長…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 某部分看來還未成長到那個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某部分?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你給我先穿上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這好像是素未謀面的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 難道你是小袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成長期真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小袋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟朋友交換?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 通過聯機線能夠實現神奇寶貝的通訊交換
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 叔叔 肉很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是最晚剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼叔叔我工作去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 我完全忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 小芽說要過她的願望要大家在一起才能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小袋你好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為雪集他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是我看到幻聽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻聽是看不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能再入手一款神奇寶貝遊戲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者只要其他人有這遊戲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是…很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨透了自己這副該死的眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長髮飄飄的小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討得仁太歡心的小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳴 我們用同一款貼紙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 很可愛對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡小芽 同時又很討厭她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴子 能過來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會使喚人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 小鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我也要玩口袋妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾玩玩又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就返璞歸真一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太你說對不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你的眼鏡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 少多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:15:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 你們倆到咱家玩真令人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要吃做完鳴子做的果凍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 是小鳴做的果凍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那樣叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 稀有寶貝就是小芽的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴 別說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳴?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 就像託夢之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得神奇寶貝是在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那裡是瑪麗兄弟的卡帶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是牛魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然有牛魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:45.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要找的不是牛魔王 而是口袋妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼剛才開始就一直站在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要小芽在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳴和她媽媽都會傷心起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是快找神奇寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 神奇寶貝 神奇寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:04.35,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（反而是你有沒有認真找）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:05.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（當然有了）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這點等著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 BOBOBO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 小小一款遊戲軟件也要貼上名字 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真小家子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時隔多年再看BOBOBO還是那麼有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信 為什麼不能沒有柏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為稀有寶貝需要用柏桑特跟剛哥爾通訊交換才能得到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手頭上沒有波桑特 需要先讓柏爾進化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳴…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳴果然一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:18:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那麼溫柔 收藏這大量的遊戲和漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那時候一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家很久沒這樣子一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 得到波桑特 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當消磨時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我的協助你有什麼回報
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要收錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好去…上學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進展如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把聯機線接上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接下來就可以進行交換了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（通訊中）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（請不要關閉電源）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:51.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（恭喜！ 稀有神奇寶貝 友情之王誕生了）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到神奇寶貝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我想小芽也一定會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的願望似乎不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有很多高興的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太跟小鳴還有小袋又重歸就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這完全是自說自話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 問 題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近小芽身邊盡是開心事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近小芽身邊盡是開心事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很久沒這麼開心過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 你剛才說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:15.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說我的心靈創傷還未痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要還有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向她道歉的事 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…也不必急於一時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
